<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/348970-is-it-like-a-recompilation-of-different">Is it like a recompilation of different stories or situations? Or is it more like an statement?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_348970'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F21251323-everyday-sexism">like</a></span>

