<div id="review_1713958754" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1713958754" />
    <a title="Jessica Frances" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/22767918-jessica-frances"><img alt="Jessica Frances" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1563076050p2/22767918.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1713958754?book_show_action=true">Jan 29, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jessica Frances" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jessica Frances" href="/user/show/22767918-jessica-frances">Jessica Frances</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9781471149207" href="/book/show/25433138-everyday-sexism">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1713958754" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13536303523608349958">This was incredible. I personally believe this should be read by everyone. Well said, well written and passionate about what it says. I learned so much and this book has been on my mind ever since. A perfect read for those who believe this whole “feminism thing” is not needed, and for those involved in the movement who would like to know what we’re up against. Every chapter is important and I will definitely be re-reading this as well as discussing these issues with family, friends and co-worker</span>
  <span id="freeText13536303523608349958" style="display:none">This was incredible. I personally believe this should be read by everyone. Well said, well written and passionate about what it says. I learned so much and this book has been on my mind ever since. A perfect read for those who believe this whole “feminism thing” is not needed, and for those involved in the movement who would like to know what we’re up against. Every chapter is important and I will definitely be re-reading this as well as discussing these issues with family, friends and co-workers. A must read.</span>
  <a data-text-id="13536303523608349958" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

